title: New York Times Bestseller - Fiction Combined - 12 January 2014
description:
Each week, any new books added to the NY Times Best-Sellers list will be added.

The New York Times Best Seller list was first published without fanfare on October 12, 1931. It consisted of five fiction and four non-fiction for the New York City region only. It is widely considered the preeminent list of best-selling books in the United States.
